   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To convert the alarm signals sent from the system to Profibus DP
a AB9001 communication gateway is used. The AB9001 gateway converts
the Modbus TCP/ IP signal sent from the network management card (NMC).</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The NMC card is required for using the AB9001 communication gateway.
The connection between the NMC and the AB9001 uses a straight Ethernet
cable (RJ45 connection).</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">A connection can then be made to the AB9001 gateway with a straight
Ethernet cable (RJ45 connection) to access the Profibus DP signals.</p>
